b'     Dear Students,      Link      Nanyang Technological University has internship positions open for prefinal year students(UG/DD/PG) from IIT Madras.  To apply for the internship, students have to submit:      1.  CV   CV has to contain updated phone numbers, roll number, email id.    2.  Research Statement    Students have to identify at least 3 faculty members from Nanyang Technological University () of their research interest and list them in the research statement. Students are advised not to contact faculty members at NTU.     3.  Official Transcripts    4.  Letter of Recommendation    5.  Copy of Passport    Send all documents to oir4@wmail.iitm.ac.in   (or)   oir4.iitm@gmail.com.   The last date for submitting applications is March 3 2016.     Mr. Arvind Sivamani  Liaison Officer (Outgoing Students)  International Relations  Office of International Relations l 2 nd Floor, IC & SR Building  Indian Institute of Technology Madras l Chennai  600 036 l INDIA  Tel: (91) 0442257 4928  Email: oir4@wmail.iitm.ac.in   Website:       '

